form.column(method='post' action='/signup')
  .form-group.col-md-5 
    h3 
      span.col-auto.badge.badge-warning
      | Registration as a buddy seeker
  if error != undefined
    .form-group.col-md-5 
      .alert.alert-danger(role="alert")
        | Error (#{error.code || "No Error code"}): #{error.message || "No error message"}
  .form-group.col-md-5 
    label(for='name')
      | Email address 
      span(style='color: red; display: inline; float: none;') 
        | *
    input.form-control(type='string' name='name' aria-describedby='nameHelp' placeholder='Enter your name' required='') 
  .form-group.col-md-5
    label(for='special_needs') My buddy needs to be able to:
    select.form-control.col-md-5(id='special_needs_skills' name='special_needs_skills' multiple)
      option(value="guide_vision_impaired") Guide a visually impaired person
      option(value="guide_blind") Guide a blind person
      option(value="psychological_support") Offer psychological support
      option(value="nursing") Do medical nursing
      option(value="handle_wheelchair") Handle a wheelchair appropriately
      option(value="sign_language") Use sign language
      option(value="trauma_awareness") Deal supportively with trauma
      option(value="neurodiversity_awareness") Deal supportively with neurodiversity
      option(value="intellectual_disability_awereness") Deal supportively with intellectual disability
      option(value="speech_with_gestures") Use speech with gestures
      option(value="LGBTQIAplus_awareness") Be supportive of LGBTQIAplus
  .form-group.col-md-5 
    label(for='email')
      | Email address 
      span(style='color: red; display: inline; float: none;') 
        | *
    input.form-control(type='email' name='email' aria-describedby='emailHelp' placeholder='Enter email' required='') 
    small#emailHelp.form-text.text-muted
    | We&apos;ll never share your email with anyone else. 
  .form-group.col-md-5
    label(for='password_1') 
      | Password 
      span(style='color: red; display: inline; float: none;') 
        | * 
    input.form-control(type='password' name='password_1' placeholder='Password' required='') 
  .form-group.col-md-5
    label(for='password_2') 
      | Confirm password 
      span(style='color: red; display: inline; float: none;') 
        | * 
    input.form-control(type='password' name='password_2' placeholder='Password' required='') 
  .form-group.col-md-5
    input(type="hidden" id="signup_type" name="signup_type" value="seeker")
    button.btn.btn-outline-warning(type='submit') 
      | Sign up
  .form-group.col-md-5 
  p.col-md-5 
    | Already a member?
    a.text-warning(href='/login') 
      | Log in